				<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/cf131c939547bd4528658ab8659b93dc?s=44&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-44 photo' height='44' width='44' />				<cite class="comment-author">					<a rel="nofollow" href="http://gidmoz.fr">gidmoz</a>
