				<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2011/11/30/11471-le-retour-a-letalon-or-pourquoi-et-comment-explique-par-ron-paul?replytocom=54262#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("comment-54262", "54262", "respond", "11471")'>Répondre</a>							</div>
